OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FA failure of allies to support the US
OL,8,Fmilitary offensive against Iran was
OL,9,F"unconscionable", the country's
OL,10,Fdefence secretary has said and warned
OL,11,F"we will remember".
OL,13,FPete Hegseth and US President Donald
OL,14,FTrump have both singled out the UK for
OL,15,Fcriticism in the past over its
OL,16,Freluctance to be drawn into the Middle
OL,17,FEast conflict.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]sD@AOUsD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
