CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FThe latest rebuke was contained in a
OL,8,Fwritten statement by Mr Hegseth to
OL,9,Fpowerful appropriations subcommittees
OL,10,Fin Congress which oversee defence
OL,11,Fspending.
OL,13,FMr Hegseth also warned there will be
OL,14,F"consequences" for Nato members that
OL,15,F"do not step up".
OL,17,FIt came as it was revealed the cost of
OL,18,Fthe Iran war had risen to around 29
OL,19,Fbillion dollars (#21.4 billion) ` up
OL,20,Ffrom the 25 billion dollars (#18.5
OL,21,Fbillion) reported nearly two weeks ago.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@NO]wD@AOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
