CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FThe mounting cost of the conflict and
OL,8,Fthe impact on US weapons stockpiles
OL,9,Fhave raised concerns on Capitol Hill.
OL,11,FMotorists in the US have also seen
OL,12,Fpetrol prices soar by more than 50%
OL,13,Fsince the outbreak of hostilities,
OL,14,Ftriggered by US and Israeli strikes.
OL,16,FIn retaliation, Iran effectively
OL,17,Fclosed the Strait of Hormuz, a vital
OL,18,Fshipping lane for oil and gas
OL,19,Fsupplies, sparking a global energy
OL,20,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
