PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FThis led the US to impose its own
OL,8,Fblockade of Iranian ports, leading to
OL,9,Fa stand-off.
OL,11,FThe soaring cost of fuel in the US has
OL,12,Ffed into domestic discontent over the
OL,13,Fwar and fuelled Republican concerns in
OL,14,Fthe run-up to the November midterm
OL,15,Felections, which will decide the make-
OL,16,Fup of Congress and a host of state
OL,17,Fgovernorships.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
