OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FBut Mr Trump has said he was not
OL,8,Fconsidering the economic cost of the
OL,9,Fwar to householders and argued the
OL,10,Fonly thing that mattered was
OL,11,Fpreventing Iran getting a nuclear
OL,12,Fweapon.
OL,14,FThere is set to be no let up after Mr
OL,15,FTrump said the Iran ceasefire was on
OL,16,F"life support" and dismissed Tehran's
OL,17,Fpeace proposal as "garbage", causing
OL,18,Foil prices to again increase sharply.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@NO]yD@SOUyD@[O]
