OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FIn his written statement, Mr Hegseth
OL,8,Fsaid Nato in the post-Cold War era had
OL,9,Fbecome "beset by freeriding" and
OL,10,Fneeded to change with allies "finally
OL,11,Fstepping up and making good on their
OL,12,Fcommitments to our collective defence".
OL,14,FHe said: "Not all allies have gotten
OL,15,Fthe message, and where they do not
OL,16,Fstep up, there will be consequences.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@\O]rD@^OUtD@fO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
