CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,F"In recent weeks, for instance, far
OL,8,Ftoo many of our Nato allies showed
OL,9,Fthat they could not be relied upon to
OL,10,Fsupport our nation's operations
OL,11,Fagainst Iran ` despite the fact that
OL,12,Fthey themselves are far more reliant
OL,13,Fon Middle East energy markets than we
OL,14,Fare and also share our interest in
OL,15,Fdenying Iran a nuclear weapons and
OL,16,Fotherwise degrading Iran's power
OL,17,Fprojection capabilities.
OL,19,F"This is unconscionable ` and we will
OL,20,Fremember."
OL,26,@oD@AOU{D@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
