PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FHe continued: "Americans want partners
OL,8,F` not dependencies. And, thanks to
OL,9,FPresident Trump's visionary
OL,10,Fleadership, that is what we are
OL,11,Fbuilding. Real partnerships and
OL,12,Falliances based on hard power.
OL,14,F"Our allies aren't powerless. They are
OL,15,Fnations capable of doing far more for
OL,16,Fthemselves than they have. It's time
OL,17,Fthey stood up, and some of them are."
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOUyD@eO]
