OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FHe hailed "model allies" including
OL,8,FIsrael, South Korea, Poland, Finland
OL,9,Fand the Baltic countries, while the UK
OL,10,Fand France were notably not mentioned.
OL,12,FMr Hegseth has previously dismissed
OL,13,Fefforts being led by the two nations
OL,14,Fto protect shipping in the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz once the conflict is over as
OL,16,F"silly".
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@XO]xD@AOUxD@GO]
