OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FThe future defensive mission would see
OL,8,Fthe UK deploy autonomous mine-hunting
OL,9,Fequipment, anti-drone systems and
OL,10,FTyphoon jets, alongside the destroyer
OL,11,FHMS Dragon.
OL,13,FThe US has already announced plans to
OL,14,Fpull 5,000 troops from Germany, while
OL,15,FMr Trump has also threatened to
OL,16,Fwithdraw military personnel from Italy
OL,17,Fand Spain over their stance on the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
