OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,FDuring the Congressional hearings, Mr
OL,8,FHegseth faced criticism from
OL,9,FRepublicans over the White House's
OL,10,Ffractious relations with long-term
OL,11,Fallies.
OL,13,FSenator Mitch McConnell, chairman of
OL,14,Fthe Senate appropriations subcommittee
OL,15,Fon defence, said: "Nato is the most
OL,16,Fimportant military alliance in world
OL,17,Fhistory.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
