PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778724213
OL,3,CRefusal by allies to back US in war
OL,4,Cagainst Iran 'unconscionable', says
OL,5,CHegseth
OL,7,F"It seems to me that a lot of the
OL,8,FEuropean countries think that we're
OL,9,Freducing our influence there, they're
OL,10,Fsort of on their own."
OL,12,FSeparately, congressman Tom Cole, the
OL,13,FRepublican chairman of the House
OL,14,Fappropriations committee, said:
OL,15,F"America First has never meant America
OL,16,Falone.
OL,18,F"American power is most effective when
OL,19,Fit's exercised in concert with like-
OL,20,Fminded nations who share our interests
OL,21,Fand our values."
